story:
Jack begins his journey,
To lands unseen and unknown.
in the wild terrain he quickly gets confused on where to go next
he needed support and luckily he found a friend of there who was also there to explore the Unseen and unknown

A map, old and dusted, both of their eyes leaned in.
An assist they needed, to unscramble the path unseen.
in the map they found a secret message that needed to be solved
secret message was very strange something that they had never seen before and they both were very worried how to solve it and luckily they found a secret way to solve it

Evidence they found on the path,
Hints to solve the riddle's wrath.
A mystery that time would unwrap.
they quickly solved the mystery and had Newfound trust that they will be able to finish their Journey
the truth was that a day that Jack was actually dreaming and he was asleep
